OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended over
OL,4,Callegations he made racist comments
OL,6,FReform deputy leader Richard Tice had
OL,7,Frefused to directly criticise Mr
OL,8,FGibbins on Sunday, accusing the media
OL,9,Fof "smearing" the party - adding he
OL,10,Fcondemned "everything that is wrong
OL,11,Fand inappropriate".
OL,13,FHowever, on Monday evening (11 May) a
OL,14,FReform spokesperson said Mr Gibbins
OL,15,Fhad been suspended from the party
OL,16,Fpending an investigation.
OL,18,FMr Gibbins will now represent the
OL,19,FHylton Castle ward as an independent.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
