OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended over
OL,4,Callegations he made racist comments
OL,6,FReform UK took control of Sunderland
OL,7,FCity Council in last week's election,
OL,8,Fwith 58 councillors voted in.
OL,10,FMeanwhile Chris Eynon, the new member
OL,11,Ffor Redhouse ward, is expected to
OL,12,Fbecome council leader after he was
OL,13,Felected leader of the Reform UK group
OL,14,Fin the city on Monday.
OL,16,FHe said: "It is a tremendous honour to
OL,17,Fhave been elected by my colleagues to
OL,18,Flead the Reform UK group following
OL,19,Fthese historic local elections.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
