OL,6,F"The people of Wearside voted for
OL,7,Fchange and we are determined to
OL,8,Fdeliver it.
OL,10,F"I look forward to leading our teams
OL,11,Fas we work tirelessly on behalf of
OL,12,Fresidents across Sunderland and begin
OL,13,Fa new chapter for our city."
